        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true'>Sum of Profit for each Product Name.  Color shows details about Sub-Category.  The marks are labeled by sum of Profit. The data is filtered on Return(Calculated), which keeps 0. The view is filtered on Product Name and Exclusions (Product Name,Sub-Category). The Product Name filter keeps 10 of 1,849 members. The Exclusions (Product Name,Sub-Category) filter keeps 1,846 members.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true'>The Docubind Bindershould be discontinued immediately as it is costing the store as much as the machines currently shoiwing as net negatives.</run>
